### 1. 测试新增学生
POST http://localhost:8085/student/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S1001",
  "name": "张三",
  "className": "计科1班",
  "age": 20
}

### 2. 测试根据学号查询学生
GET http://localhost:8085/student/S1001
Accept: application/json

### 3. 测试查询所有学生
GET http://localhost:8085/student/all
Accept: application/json

### 4. 测试根据班级查询学生
GET http://localhost:8085/student/list?className=计科1班
Accept: application/json

### 5. 测试删除学生
DELETE http://localhost:8085/student/S1001
Accept: application/json

### 6. 测试新增考勤记录
POST http://localhost:8085/attendance/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "studentId": 3,
  "checkInTime": "2026-04-15T08:50:00",
  "seatRow": 2,
  "seatCol": 3,
  "status": "NORMAL",
  "ip": "192.168.1.10"
}

### 7. 测试查询所有考勤记录
GET http://localhost:8085/attendance/all
Accept: application/json

### 8. 测试根据学生ID查询考勤
GET http://localhost:8085/attendance/student/3
Accept: application/json

### 9. 测试根据课程ID查询考勤
GET http://localhost:8085/attendance/course/1
Accept: application/json